  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Levi Panorama is on a half-board basis.</p>
<p>Each morning a varied breakfast buffet is served with a wide selection of fruits, yogurts, cold meats and cheeses, breads, pastries, eggs, and bacon.</p>
<p>In the evening you can enjoy a varied three-course buffet with a variety of starters, hot dishes, a salad buffet, a selection of desserts, and after-dinner tea or coffee.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast is included for all guests arriving before Christmas, for a Christmas celebration meal with games and music. Please note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
